item.title: ET
item.description: score:93 Chances: Energy Transfer’s fourth-quarter earnings are likely to have benefited from strong volumes and the completed acquisition of Crestwood. The company’s potentially needle-moving Lake Charles LNG project continues to make slow progress. The Investment in USAC segment offers compression services to its customers, enhancing crude oil production through artificial lift processes.
